PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Public Works of Hugo C. Stahl, of Williams Lake, British Columbia, as a director of the Board of Directors of Canada Mortgage and Housing Corporation, from outside the public service of Canada, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Ross Marks, whose term has expired.
